---
title: Melty Double Red Pepper Panini with Roasted Asparagus & Herbed Aioli
description: When you’re pressed for time, there’s really nothing better than panini sandwiches. This version features double deliciousness with roasted bell pepper and a creamy roasted red pepper spread—but that’s not all! Sautéed zucchini and garlicky aioli are tucked in too, melded together with mozzarella between golden slices of sourdough. Roasted potato wedges are served on the side with extra aioli, and it all comes together in about 30 minutes. Yay for speedy panini!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/642aef4303dae7c75c0aecc8-cb3408d7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/646e34a35a5d033baf4b14c4.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/melty-double-red-pepper-panini-646e34a35a5d033baf4b14c4
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
  calories: 690 kcal
  fat: 41 g
